# rmdownloader agent configuration (key=value, one per line).
# OPTIONAL — you can skip this file and run:  Agent.exe <key>
# The agent only makes OUTBOUND calls to 'server', so it works behind home NAT with
# no port-forwarding or tunnel.
#
# For zero-touch onboarding, put the site's shared ENROLL_KEY here as 'token' and ship
# THIS SAME folder to every PC — each one auto-registers itself (by machine id, shown as
# the hostname) and appears in the web picker. No per-PC setup, no editing the server.

server=https://dos.argonar.co

# The site's ENROLL_KEY (same on every PC), or a per-PC static token from rm_agents().
token=CHANGE-THIS-TO-THE-SITE-ENROLL-KEY

# Optional sandbox: restrict all access to this folder and below. Empty = whole machine.
# root=C:\shared
root=
